    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Freight cars, with open or closed tops, containing hoppers for transporting bulk cargo, as coal or grain, that can be quickly discharged through their bottoms.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
